        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\nskinparam componentStyle rectangle\nskinparam arrowColor DimGray\n\ntitle Threat Modeling: Вектори на атака и защитни слоеве\n\nactor \&quot;Злонамерен потребител\&quot; as Attacker #FFCCCC\n\npackage \&quot;EcoProject Security Boundaries\&quot; {\n    \n    component \&quot;Frontend (React)\&quot; as UI #LightGreen\n    note right of UI: Защита срещу XSS атаки\\nчрез React DOM escaping\n    \n    component \&quot;API Gateway / Controller\&quot; as API #LightGreen\n    note right of API: Rate Limiting &amp;\\nCORS Policies\n    \n    component \&quot;IAssistantPromptSafetyService\&quot; as PromptSafety #LightGreen\n    note right of PromptSafety: Детекция и блокиране на\\nPrompt Injection\n    \n    component \&quot;IAssistantProvenancePolicyService\&quot; as TrustPolicy #LightGreen\n    note right of TrustPolicy: Блокиране на Quarantined domains\\nи несигурни източници\n    \n    database \&quot;SQL Server\&quot; as DB #LightBlue\n}\n\ncloud \&quot;AI Providers\\n(Gemini / OpenAI)\&quot; as AI\n\n&#39; Attack Vectors\nAttacker -[#Red,thickness=2]-&gt; UI : \&quot;XSS Payload\&quot;\nAttacker -[#Red,thickness=2]-&gt; API : \&quot;SQL Injection\&quot;\nAttacker -[#Red,thickness=2]-&gt; PromptSafety : \&quot;Prompt Injection / Jailbreak\&quot;\nAttacker -[#Red,thickness=2]-&gt; TrustPolicy : \&quot;Манипулирани външни данни\&quot;\n\n&#39; Safe Flow\nUI --&gt; API : \&quot;Sanitized Input\&quot;\nAPI --&gt; PromptSafety : \&quot;Проверка\&quot;\nPromptSafety --&gt; TrustPolicy : \&quot;Безопасен текст\&quot;\nTrustPolicy --&gt; AI : \&quot;Сигурна комуникация\&quot;\nAPI --&gt; DB : \&quot;EF Core (Параметризирани заявки)\&quot;\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="MQRGQCEITAgNSEkw5GLr-1">
